    oc:hasSection [ a oc:Section ;
            oc:hasContent [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                    oc:textContent "Reduce PDF file sizes for easier sharing, faster loading, and efficient storage." ] ;
            oc:hasSubsection [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasSubsection [ a oc:Section ;
                            oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                    oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                    oc:codeContent """## Additional Optimizations

### Font Optimization
- [ ] Subset fonts (remove unused characters)
- [ ] Convert to standard fonts where possible
- [ ] Remove duplicate font instances

### Structure Optimization
- [ ] Remove unused objects
- [ ] Clean up metadata
- [ ] Linearize for web (fast web view)
- [ ] Remove bookmarks (optional)
- [ ] Remove comments/annotations (optional)

### Content Removal (Caution)
- [ ] Remove hidden layers
- [ ] Remove JavaScript
- [ ] Remove form fields
- [ ] Remove embedded files
""" ;
                                    oc:codeLanguage "markdown" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                    oc:sourceLocation "lines 139-159" ] ;
                            oc:sectionLevel 3 ;
                            oc:sectionOrder 2 ;
                            oc:sectionTitle "Content Optimization" ],
                        [ a oc:Section ;
                            oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                    oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                    oc:codeContent """## Image Compression Settings

### Resolution Reduction
| Target | DPI | Use For |
|--------|-----|---------|
| Screen | 72 | Web viewing |
| eBook | 150 | Digital documents |
| Print-basic | 200 | Office printing |
| Print-quality | 300 | Professional print |
| Original | N/A | No reduction |

### Format Conversion
| From | To | Savings | Quality Impact |
|------|-----|---------|----------------|
| TIFF | JPEG | 70-90% | Some loss |
| PNG | JPEG | 50-80% | Some loss |
| BMP | JPEG | 90%+ | Some loss |
| JPEG | JPEG (recompress) | 20-50% | Cumulative loss |

### Quality Levels
| Setting | JPEG Quality | Visual Impact |
|---------|--------------|---------------|
| Maximum | 90-100 | Imperceptible |
| High | 75-89 | Minimal |
| Medium | 50-74 | Noticeable on zoom |
| Low | 25-49 | Visible artifacts |
""" ;
                                    oc:codeLanguage "markdown" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                    oc:sourceLocation "lines 109-136" ] ;
                            oc:sectionLevel 3 ;
                            oc:sectionOrder 1 ;
                            oc:sectionTitle "Image Optimization" ] ;
                    oc:sectionLevel 2 ;
                    oc:sectionOrder 4 ;
                    oc:sectionTitle "Compression Techniques" ],
