                [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasSubsection [ a oc:Section ;
                            oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                    oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                    oc:codeContent """## Quality Comparison Guide

### Image Quality at Different Levels

**Original (300 DPI, no compression)**
- Sharp at all zoom levels
- File size: Large

**High Quality (200 DPI, JPEG 85%)**
- Sharp at 100-200% zoom
- Minor softening at high zoom
- File size: Medium-large

**Medium Quality (150 DPI, JPEG 70%)**
- Good at 100% zoom
- Noticeable softening at 200%+
- File size: Medium

**Low Quality (96 DPI, JPEG 50%)**
- Acceptable at 100%
- Pixelation visible
- File size: Small

### Text Remains Sharp
Note: Text (when vector) remains crisp at all compression levels.
Only embedded text images are affected.
""" ;
                                    oc:codeLanguage "markdown" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                    oc:sourceLocation "lines 267-294" ] ;
                            oc:sectionLevel 3 ;
                            oc:sectionOrder 1 ;
                            oc:sectionTitle "Before/After Guide" ] ;
                    oc:sectionLevel 2 ;
                    oc:sectionOrder 7 ;
                    oc:sectionTitle "Quality Comparison" ],
                [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasSubsection [ a oc:Section ;
                            oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                    oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                    oc:codeContent """## Compression Strategy: [Document Name]

### Current State
- File size: 150 MB
- Pages: 200
- Issue: Too large for email (limit: 25 MB)

### Target
- Max size: 20 MB
- Maintain readability

### Recommended Approach
1. **Images**: Reduce to 150 DPI, JPEG 70%
   - Expected savings: ~100 MB
2. **Fonts**: Subset embedded fonts
   - Expected savings: ~5 MB
3. **Cleanup**: Remove metadata, optimize structure
   - Expected savings: ~5 MB

### Expected Result
- Final size: ~20 MB
- Quality: Good for screen/general use
""" ;
                                    oc:codeLanguage "markdown" ;
